    10  FILLER                    PIC X(01) VALUE ':'.
    10  WS-TIMESTAMP-TM-MM        PIC 9(02).
    10  FILLER                    PIC X(01) VALUE ':'.
    10  WS-TIMESTAMP-TM-SS        PIC 9(02).
    10  FILLER                    PIC X(01) VALUE '.'.
    10  WS-TIMESTAMP-TM-MS6       PIC 9(06).
